</div>
			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">International Working People's Association</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:252px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Freiheit.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Freiheit.png/250px-Freiheit.png" width="250" height="376" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Freiheit.png/375px-Freiheit.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b9/Freiheit.png/500px-Freiheit.png 2x" data-file-width="808" data-file-height="1214" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Freiheit.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"></a></div>
Cover of <i>Freiheit,</i> weekly newspaper edited by Johann Most.</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>The <b>International Working People's Association</b> (<b>IWPA</b>), sometimes known as the "<b>Black International</b>," was an international <a href="/wiki/Anarchist" title="Anarchist" class="mw-redirect">anarchist</a> political organization established in 1881 at a convention held in <a href="/wiki/London,_England" title="London, England" class="mw-redirect">London, England</a>. In America the group is best remembered as the political organization uniting <a href="/wiki/Albert_Parsons" title="Albert Parsons">Albert Parsons</a>, <a href="/wiki/August_Spies" title="August Spies">August Spies</a>, and other anarchist leaders prosecuted in the wake of the 1886 <a href="/wiki/Haymarket_affair" title="Haymarket affair">Haymarket bombing</a> in <a href="/wiki/Chicago,_Illinois" title="Chicago, Illinois" class="mw-redirect">Chicago</a>.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
